          <h1>My Belbin Team Roles</h1>
          <p>
            A snapshot of how I naturally tend to contribute in a team context,
            based on the Belbin Team Roles framework. This isn’t a fixed label,
            but a way of understanding strengths, potential blind spots and how
            I work best with others.
          </p>
